            <thetext>The splitpane widget itself does not include borders it&#39;s the appearance theme which sets the &quot;splitpane&quot; decorator for the splitpane widget in the &quot;Modern&quot; theme. This appearance is consistent for the &quot;Modern&quot; theme and since it&#39;s a theme this is only one of the theming possibilities of this widget.
